{"tid":2167264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工會轟拒堵無薪假漏洞","createTime":"2020-08-21T03:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T04:21:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"98e60f6adb3566cfd26a921b61e2a3a392264852","tid":2167264,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/QTQZRICXMVD2TK23WDMDBCCLBY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FQTQZRICXMVD2TK23WDMDBCCLBY%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuwHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=82105cd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FQTQZRICXMVD2TK23WDMDBCCLBY%2F&h=8262173b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/QTQZRICXMVD2TK23WDMDBCCLBY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n工會轟拒堵無薪假漏洞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zYFkTQEMMymvv73Xc3l-KizeSSE=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CCFJUZCXS5BXFOGQCUOBOGHFZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzYFkTQEMMymvv73Xc3l-KizeSSE%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCCFJUZCXS5BXFOGQCUOBOGHFZY.jpg&h=37b32377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蒙兆達<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】保就業計劃屢被批評縱容僱主逼員工放無薪假，政府前日發新聞稿，指正在或被要求放無薪假的員工不會視作有支薪僱員，故不會計入承諾受薪僱員人數。勞福局局長羅致光昨表示，如僱員只有部份日子放無薪假，就要「睇吓出糧出成點」，意味僱主或可繼續領取補貼。工會炮轟政府大玩語言偽術，未堵塞漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅：睇吓出糧出成點<br />\n<br />\n羅致光稱，若僱員只是部份日子放無薪假，要「睇吓出糧出成點」，以及獲得工資補貼後，僱主有否減少其無薪假。他強調計劃要靠僱主負起責任，「如果逐個僱主去睇政策，我。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟總幹事蒙兆達批評，計劃仍舊無限制僱主逼放無薪假，「政府只係要求員工係支薪僱員，但冇規定佢要支幾多薪，即係一個。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"901d875cf3a9028725ed26ed2760781e552b281b","tid":2167264,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb17df3fd24f236400221d6a0eb5effe3112c3f4","tid":2167264,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:05:43.000Z","msg":"政府：睇死你地驚無左份工多過無錢收"},{"pid":"6a6b47d7d262354312ca9327a31a763303b2918a","tid":2167264,"uid":152643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"噤錯負評有冇得取消的"},{"pid":"8b82cb45761a635381d8bf18748bec2bd12815c8","tid":2167264,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"羅致光叻撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ebf88549b89280392ea5418fbe3941fcb39ea1","tid":2167264,"uid":38528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"依家先諗到? 當時政府一出全香港市民都諗到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6106915ab381918ac934fa65c785bca5e978836f","tid":2167264,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:13:51.000Z","msg":"返一個鐘照拎補貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455353d03990e5ba8fffe554a7d03f4be8a3e589","tid":2167264,"uid":143016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:18:08.000Z","msg":"如果無拎津貼又無薪假又點睇？ 窮死了"},{"pid":"16a7dd75fd815b4ffbd027cf389b47ce86f507eb","tid":2167264,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"佢明顯係保老細 但講到明會比人屌 <br />\n所以改個閪名呃你啲傻人 <br />\n以為政府會企係打工仔一邊<br />\n實際就掛羊頭賣狗肉"}]}